            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Suge de mea si vis vita <lb n="2"/>rem nemo vita <del rend="erasure"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></del> tene me Verul&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt; </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> tangat |(denarios) XXXXV Verule </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> pr<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>esta</abbr></expan> si me amas no&amp;lt;l=N&amp;gt;i despicer<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> Seriole </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <surplus>i</surplus>v<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>ltum</abbr></expan> meum <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>omo</abbr></expan> <lb n="2"/>sum ne d&amp;lt;a&amp;gt; </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>computu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftträger: Trinkbecher mit Ritzinschrift (Graffito). Inschriftengattung: Widmungsinschrift. Textwiedergabe nach Blänsdorf.</p>
            </div>
